1
00:00:01,000 --> 00:00:04,440
THIS DRAMA IS CREATED
FOR ENTERTAINMENT PURPOSES

2
00:00:04,520 --> 00:00:07,680
ALL CHARACTERS, SETTINGS
AND EVENTS ARE ENTIRELY FICTITIOUS

3
00:00:07,760 --> 00:00:10,920
THERE IS NO INTENT TO REFERENCE
ANY ORGANIZATIONS OR INDIVIDUALS

4
00:03:07,440 --> 00:03:09,160
<i>I once let you risk your life.</i>

5
00:03:09,240 --> 00:03:11,240
<i>This time, I'll put my life in your hands.</i>

6
00:03:11,760 --> 00:03:12,840
<i>I'm not going soft, Sarge.</i>

7
00:03:12,920 --> 00:03:15,280
But I still want you to lead the team.

8
00:03:16,240 --> 00:03:18,560
Come on. Hug each other.

9
00:03:20,520 --> 00:03:24,240
The plan to wipe out Tiangmon's online
gambling and call center scam network.

10
00:03:25,960 --> 00:03:27,200
This is the place.

11
00:03:28,080 --> 00:03:29,680
<i>May I have your phone?</i>

12
00:03:31,920 --> 00:03:33,840
<i>This time, I've got a bad feeling.</i>

13
00:03:44,520 --> 00:03:45,760
Come on. Don't complain.

14
00:03:48,960 --> 00:03:51,200
Sit here.

15
00:03:51,280 --> 00:03:52,320
Sit down.

16
00:03:56,120 --> 00:03:57,200
Please, I want to go home.

17
00:03:57,280 --> 00:03:58,800
I don't want this job anymore.

18
00:03:58,880 --> 00:04:01,160
Please let me go.
I won't tell anyone. Please.

19
00:04:01,240 --> 00:04:02,480
You won't tell anyone?

20
00:04:02,560 --> 00:04:04,080
- You won't tell anyone, huh?
- Hey!

21
00:04:04,160 --> 00:04:05,160
- Huh?
- Hey.

22
00:04:05,240 --> 00:04:07,000
From now on, you follow every order.

23
00:04:07,800 --> 00:04:10,320
If you hit your target,
you eat and sleep well.

24
00:04:10,400 --> 00:04:11,800
If you miss it,

25
00:04:11,880 --> 00:04:14,720
or ask for help and try to run,
this is what happens.

26
00:04:14,800 --> 00:04:16,640
Damn, they really are brutal.

27
00:04:16,720 --> 00:04:18,720
Think Moh and Akki will make it?

28
00:04:19,240 --> 00:04:20,240
No idea.

29
00:04:21,160 --> 00:04:23,800
Did you search them all?

30
00:04:23,880 --> 00:04:24,760
All done.

31
00:04:25,280 --> 00:04:26,440
Then take them inside.

32
00:04:26,520 --> 00:04:27,360
Hey.

33
00:04:27,440 --> 00:04:29,040
- Go. Get up.
- Get up.

34
00:04:29,120 --> 00:04:30,080
Go.

35
00:04:30,160 --> 00:04:31,000
- Walk.
- Get up.

36
00:04:31,080 --> 00:04:32,200
Uh, yeah.

37
00:04:32,840 --> 00:04:34,600
Hey, get up.

38
00:04:34,680 --> 00:04:36,560
- Oh, what?
- Get up.

39
00:04:36,640 --> 00:04:37,880
Easy, bro.

40
00:04:38,520 --> 00:04:39,560
- Get up!
- Yes.

41
00:04:40,120 --> 00:04:41,200
- Hey.
- Whoa.

42
00:04:42,200 --> 00:04:44,720
Hey, hey. Why are you going with them?

43
00:04:52,680 --> 00:04:54,040
- Whoa, Dan.
- Just a bit.

44
00:04:54,120 --> 00:04:55,080
- Easy.
- Almost there.

45
00:04:56,080 --> 00:04:58,160
- Hurry up. That hurts.
- Almost there.

46
00:04:58,240 --> 00:04:59,520
- Whoa.
- Almost there.

47
00:05:02,360 --> 00:05:04,840
I'm falling. I'm falling. Move.

48
00:05:06,520 --> 00:05:09,080
That was close. Too close, man.

49
00:05:12,880 --> 00:05:14,720
- How much do you weigh, bro?
- Huh?

50
00:05:14,800 --> 00:05:15,920
My shoulder's about to give out.

51
00:05:16,000 --> 00:05:18,320
Hey, look at me. You're still complaining?

52
00:05:23,840 --> 00:05:25,520
Akki's in position.

53
00:05:25,600 --> 00:05:27,240
Juk, Dan, are you in yet?

54
00:05:28,200 --> 00:05:30,720
We're in. Mission's about to start.

55
00:05:30,800 --> 00:05:31,840
Hurry up.

56
00:05:34,240 --> 00:05:36,640
- Wait.
- What now?

57
00:05:36,720 --> 00:05:37,960
- The bag.
- What bag?

58
00:05:38,040 --> 00:05:39,840
- The bomb bag.
- The bag's…

59
00:05:46,520 --> 00:05:47,480
Up there.

60
00:05:48,480 --> 00:05:49,600
I forgot it.

61
00:05:50,400 --> 00:05:51,960
Damn it. I really forgot.

62
00:05:52,040 --> 00:05:53,680
- You forgot it?
- Yeah, up there.

63
00:05:53,760 --> 00:05:56,920
All the way up there.
I shouldn't have forgotten it.

64
00:05:57,440 --> 00:05:58,840
It's your turn.

65
00:06:05,480 --> 00:06:07,160
Hurry up. I can't, Juk.

66
00:06:07,240 --> 00:06:08,600
Juk. Juk…

67
00:06:12,480 --> 00:06:15,280
Juk, Dan, what the hell are you two doing?

68
00:06:18,560 --> 00:06:19,920
Sit.

69
00:06:20,560 --> 00:06:21,880
What's wrong with him?

70
00:06:23,760 --> 00:06:25,120
Even if you're new,

71
00:06:25,640 --> 00:06:27,720
you still have to hit the same target.

72
00:06:27,800 --> 00:06:28,760
Got it?

73
00:06:31,080 --> 00:06:34,560
Bro, I'm not good at lying.

74
00:06:35,360 --> 00:06:36,360
Hey.

75
00:06:37,040 --> 00:06:38,880
If you're really scared of dying,

76
00:06:39,840 --> 00:06:41,280
you'll learn fast.

77
00:06:41,360 --> 00:06:42,720
Just do it.

78
00:06:43,480 --> 00:06:44,480
All right.

79
00:06:47,440 --> 00:06:49,240
Play along and let them lower their guard.

80
00:06:54,720 --> 00:06:58,160
Akki, this is just one room.

81
00:06:58,240 --> 00:07:00,880
I saw many more earlier.

82
00:07:00,960 --> 00:07:01,880
I think this place

83
00:07:02,400 --> 00:07:04,480
is their golden goose.

84
00:07:04,560 --> 00:07:06,480
It's their cash cow.

85
00:07:08,280 --> 00:07:12,360
Don't worry.
I've got this. It's my specialty.

86
00:07:15,200 --> 00:07:16,040
Hey!

87
00:07:18,440 --> 00:07:20,560
Are you done chatting?

88
00:07:22,200 --> 00:07:25,840
If you don't work, I'll deal with you.

89
00:07:26,360 --> 00:07:28,840
How did you manage to step on the table?

90
00:07:29,920 --> 00:07:30,920
I'm a badass.

91
00:07:31,760 --> 00:07:32,720
Keep going.

92
00:07:41,680 --> 00:07:43,280
Focus.

93
00:07:43,360 --> 00:07:44,760
Hurry up.

94
00:07:47,960 --> 00:07:48,800
Hurry.

95
00:08:34,440 --> 00:08:36,600
Auntie, please click

96
00:08:36,679 --> 00:08:39,280
the link I sent, fill in your info,

97
00:08:39,360 --> 00:08:42,600
and 200,000 <i>baht</i>
will be transferred to your account.

98
00:08:49,400 --> 00:08:51,280
Did you get in the system yet?

99
00:08:51,800 --> 00:08:54,680
Give me a sec.
They have multi-layer firewall.

100
00:08:55,200 --> 00:08:56,040
Hurry.

101
00:09:02,840 --> 00:09:05,640
Too late, Akki. Hurry up.

102
00:09:08,840 --> 00:09:10,600
What, Auntie?

103
00:09:10,680 --> 00:09:13,760
I told you I'm not a scammer.

104
00:09:13,840 --> 00:09:17,000
If you don't believe me, call the police.

105
00:09:17,080 --> 00:09:19,120
I'll send the address. Come here.

106
00:09:19,200 --> 00:09:20,240
Hey.

107
00:09:21,160 --> 00:09:22,640
Why are you yelling?

108
00:09:23,560 --> 00:09:27,080
She doesn't believe us.
She thinks we're scammers.

109
00:09:27,600 --> 00:09:29,760
It's been an hour.

110
00:09:29,840 --> 00:09:31,840
I still haven't closed.

111
00:09:31,920 --> 00:09:35,840
And she's super…

112
00:09:39,600 --> 00:09:40,920
annoying.

113
00:09:42,600 --> 00:09:43,560
Annoying?

114
00:09:46,360 --> 00:09:48,560
Everyone, look.

115
00:09:48,640 --> 00:09:52,160
If you can't hit your target,
this is what happens.

116
00:09:52,240 --> 00:09:54,560
I told you,

117
00:09:54,640 --> 00:09:56,240
- I can't lie.
- Hey, hey.

118
00:09:56,320 --> 00:09:58,360
Hey. What's your problem?

119
00:09:58,440 --> 00:10:02,040
Whoa. You causing trouble? Huh?

120
00:10:02,120 --> 00:10:04,200
- Huh? Come here.
- Ouch.

121
00:10:04,720 --> 00:10:05,800
You wanna try me?

122
00:10:07,760 --> 00:10:08,720
Hurry up.

123
00:10:11,040 --> 00:10:12,200
What's happening there?

124
00:10:13,480 --> 00:10:14,880
There are some problems.

125
00:10:18,200 --> 00:10:19,400
But still under control.

126
00:10:42,520 --> 00:10:43,720
All set?

127
00:10:43,800 --> 00:10:45,200
Bombs are planted.

128
00:10:45,280 --> 00:10:47,280
Nice. Take this.

129
00:10:47,360 --> 00:10:48,920
Take it.

130
00:10:49,000 --> 00:10:50,240
- Wear it.
- Why don't you do it yourself?

131
00:10:50,320 --> 00:10:52,000
Oh, look.

132
00:10:52,080 --> 00:10:54,080
It's so high. I'm short.

133
00:10:54,160 --> 00:10:56,040
- Fine. I'll do it.
- Hey.

134
00:10:56,120 --> 00:10:57,840
You always order me around.

135
00:10:57,920 --> 00:10:59,480
You're complaining now?

136
00:11:01,720 --> 00:11:02,920
- Here.
- Which wire?

137
00:11:03,000 --> 00:11:04,480
Here. This one.

138
00:11:04,560 --> 00:11:06,160
Oh. Here. This one.

139
00:11:06,760 --> 00:11:08,040
Which one, really?

140
00:11:08,600 --> 00:11:11,640
- Hey, wait for the signal. I'll ask Akki.
- Why didn't you say it?

141
00:11:12,280 --> 00:11:15,920
Akki. Hello. Yeah, how's it going?

142
00:11:16,000 --> 00:11:17,600
We're ready here.

143
00:11:18,800 --> 00:11:20,360
Hold on. Give me a sec.

144
00:11:25,440 --> 00:11:28,640
I think you can be prepared now.
Wait for his signal.

145
00:11:29,760 --> 00:11:30,600
Yeah.

146
00:11:34,080 --> 00:11:35,400
Dan, cut the power.

147
00:11:35,480 --> 00:11:36,200
Cut.

148
00:11:36,280 --> 00:11:39,000
All right. Done.

149
00:11:39,080 --> 00:11:39,920
Huh?

150
00:11:40,800 --> 00:11:41,880
- Here.
- Ouch!

151
00:11:45,560 --> 00:11:46,720
Why's the power out?

152
00:11:47,480 --> 00:11:49,520
Next, your life goes out.

153
00:11:51,240 --> 00:11:52,800
Everyone, run!

154
00:11:52,880 --> 00:11:54,040
We, the Seven Legends,

155
00:11:54,960 --> 00:11:56,120
will handle this!

156
00:11:56,200 --> 00:11:57,240
Hey!

157
00:12:08,920 --> 00:12:10,240
- Hey! Go check.
- Hey.

158
00:12:10,320 --> 00:12:11,720
Why's the power out?

159
00:12:41,560 --> 00:12:43,360
- Hey, hey, hey!
- Hey.

160
00:12:43,440 --> 00:12:44,600
- Calm down.
- Stop.

161
00:12:44,680 --> 00:12:46,520
- Stop. Calm down.
- Follow the others.

162
00:12:46,600 --> 00:12:47,440
Run.

163
00:12:47,520 --> 00:12:49,200
You bastard!

164
00:12:50,160 --> 00:12:51,200
Please.

165
00:12:51,280 --> 00:12:53,440
- Let me do it.
- Hey, Moh.

166
00:12:53,520 --> 00:12:54,920
Stop, stop.

167
00:13:04,480 --> 00:13:06,760
Don't, don't. Don't!

168
00:13:06,840 --> 00:13:08,520
Here.

169
00:13:12,800 --> 00:13:13,920
Hey.

170
00:13:17,200 --> 00:13:18,480
You're brutal.

171
00:13:19,520 --> 00:13:20,640
Go.

172
00:13:22,000 --> 00:13:22,960
Go.

173
00:13:24,000 --> 00:13:25,760
- Yeah!
- Yeah!

174
00:13:25,840 --> 00:13:27,080
Hey, over there!

175
00:13:27,160 --> 00:13:28,480
- Get them!
- Hurry up.

176
00:13:45,760 --> 00:13:46,760
Hey, why are they here?

177
00:13:46,840 --> 00:13:48,040
Hey, stop!

178
00:13:48,120 --> 00:13:50,160
I said stop! Stop!

179
00:13:51,120 --> 00:13:52,040
Hey, kill them!

180
00:13:52,120 --> 00:13:53,320
I'm here to help, bro.

181
00:14:08,480 --> 00:14:09,600
All clear.

182
00:14:10,480 --> 00:14:11,960
Damn.

183
00:14:12,040 --> 00:14:13,640
The real deal.

184
00:14:13,720 --> 00:14:15,600
It's not your time to die yet.

185
00:14:15,680 --> 00:14:19,160
You're lucky I showed up.
Otherwise, you'd be done.

186
00:14:19,240 --> 00:14:20,960
Why didn't you come tomorrow?

187
00:14:21,040 --> 00:14:21,880
That means?

188
00:14:21,960 --> 00:14:23,440
I don't know. Someone said that.

189
00:14:23,520 --> 00:14:24,720
You shouldn't have said that.

190
00:14:24,800 --> 00:14:25,880
Hey, Akki.

191
00:14:25,960 --> 00:14:28,120
- How is it? On plan?
- Oh.

192
00:14:28,200 --> 00:14:30,080
I infected their whole network.

193
00:14:30,160 --> 00:14:32,200
Every gambling site is completely dead.

194
00:14:33,520 --> 00:14:34,360
And…

195
00:14:34,440 --> 00:14:35,120
- Nice.
- And?

196
00:14:35,200 --> 00:14:37,520
I also got critical intel,

197
00:14:37,600 --> 00:14:39,680
enough to lead us straight to Phoenix.

198
00:14:41,360 --> 00:14:42,840
- That's sick.
- Bro,

199
00:14:42,920 --> 00:14:44,480
all bombs are planted.

200
00:14:45,000 --> 00:14:46,680
This place is gonna be rubble.

201
00:14:50,000 --> 00:14:51,840
Hey, kill them all!

202
00:14:51,920 --> 00:14:52,880
Kla!

203
00:14:53,960 --> 00:14:56,440
Wait, who's shooting downstairs?

204
00:14:56,960 --> 00:14:58,840
Hey. One, two, three, four.

205
00:14:59,560 --> 00:15:01,240
Tangkuay and Kla.

206
00:15:01,320 --> 00:15:02,800
- Yeah.
- They're fine. Let's go home.

207
00:15:02,880 --> 00:15:04,000
- Hey!
- We can't.

208
00:15:04,080 --> 00:15:05,320
- Go help them!
- Yeah.

209
00:15:05,400 --> 00:15:06,960
- What are you waiting for? Go.
- Go.

210
00:15:11,640 --> 00:15:12,680
Run!

211
00:15:32,560 --> 00:15:33,400
Hey.

212
00:15:33,480 --> 00:15:35,360
I'm out of ammo. Where are they?

213
00:15:35,440 --> 00:15:36,680
I don't know.

214
00:15:36,760 --> 00:15:38,240
Oh? We're screwed.

215
00:15:45,520 --> 00:15:47,080
We're here.

216
00:15:48,800 --> 00:15:50,120
Let's take every last one.

217
00:15:53,520 --> 00:15:54,560
Yeah.

218
00:16:38,840 --> 00:16:39,920
Hey, Sarge.

219
00:16:40,440 --> 00:16:42,320
It's been ten years.

220
00:16:42,960 --> 00:16:45,880
I never thought we'd meet like this.

221
00:16:49,440 --> 00:16:50,880
Me neither.

222
00:16:52,840 --> 00:16:54,640
The kid I saved

223
00:16:55,520 --> 00:16:58,000
and paid to have good education

224
00:16:59,400 --> 00:17:02,800
ends up doing dirty work for Phoenix,

225
00:17:02,880 --> 00:17:04,720
hurting innocent people.

226
00:17:05,760 --> 00:17:08,599
If I knew that kid would end up like this,

227
00:17:10,040 --> 00:17:11,640
I'd have left her in that brothel.

228
00:17:11,720 --> 00:17:12,720
Sarge.

229
00:17:16,400 --> 00:17:17,359
Yes.

230
00:17:20,079 --> 00:17:22,000
I was just a broken kid,

231
00:17:23,240 --> 00:17:25,200
prostituting myself to survive,

232
00:17:26,720 --> 00:17:29,440
beaten by trash men.

233
00:17:31,560 --> 00:17:33,520
If you hadn't saved me,

234
00:17:34,040 --> 00:17:35,360
I'd be dead.

235
00:17:35,880 --> 00:17:37,040
Let's take a photo.

236
00:17:39,560 --> 00:17:41,640
One, two, three.

237
00:17:42,640 --> 00:17:43,480
One, two, three.

238
00:17:44,480 --> 00:17:46,080
Okay.

239
00:17:50,080 --> 00:17:52,720
Sarge, let's celebrate tonight.

240
00:17:52,800 --> 00:17:56,480
I'm ready to follow my dream
and repay your kindness.

241
00:18:01,200 --> 00:18:02,960
I got a job.

242
00:18:03,480 --> 00:18:06,040
It pays well.

243
00:18:06,120 --> 00:18:08,680
My boss adores me.

244
00:18:10,520 --> 00:18:13,560
From now on, I'll take care of you.

245
00:18:13,640 --> 00:18:15,960
I'll be a good wife

246
00:18:16,560 --> 00:18:18,040
and you'll live comfortably.

247
00:18:18,120 --> 00:18:21,360
So you don't have to live
on a lousy government salary.

248
00:18:25,840 --> 00:18:28,680
Praew, listen. Sit down.

249
00:18:31,240 --> 00:18:33,080
You've graduated.

250
00:18:33,880 --> 00:18:36,080
You have a bright future ahead of you.

251
00:18:37,320 --> 00:18:38,800
I'm proud of you.

252
00:18:40,400 --> 00:18:41,520
But I think

253
00:18:43,560 --> 00:18:45,680
you shouldn't sink your life
with someone like me.

254
00:18:46,880 --> 00:18:48,360
I have no future.

255
00:18:52,320 --> 00:18:55,960
But my whole life,
I've only had you, Sarge.

256
00:18:57,520 --> 00:18:59,440
Thank you so much…

257
00:19:01,000 --> 00:19:03,000
for the love you have for me.

258
00:19:04,440 --> 00:19:05,400
But…

259
00:19:06,800 --> 00:19:10,120
you should save that love
for someone who deserves it.

260
00:19:15,560 --> 00:19:16,920
Good luck, Praew.

261
00:19:19,080 --> 00:19:20,040
Sarge!

262
00:19:21,080 --> 00:19:22,160
Sarge!

263
00:19:27,360 --> 00:19:29,000
Since that day,

264
00:19:29,080 --> 00:19:31,200
you left me
as if you were disgusted by me.

265
00:19:32,760 --> 00:19:34,840
Like you knew what I had been through.

266
00:19:38,520 --> 00:19:39,520
Why?

267
00:19:42,120 --> 00:19:44,160
Why did you leave me?

268
00:19:46,200 --> 00:19:48,240
Couldn't you even say you loved me?

269
00:19:50,680 --> 00:19:53,080
You thought I was disgusting, right?

270
00:19:56,440 --> 00:19:57,440
No.

271
00:19:59,280 --> 00:20:01,000
I never despised you.

272
00:20:03,280 --> 00:20:05,840
I didn't want you to stay with me because…

273
00:20:07,720 --> 00:20:09,280
I just didn't love you that way.

274
00:20:11,840 --> 00:20:16,120
I didn't want you to stay with me.
I didn't want to lie.

275
00:20:18,120 --> 00:20:19,480
So I walked away.

276
00:20:22,040 --> 00:20:23,920
Then you chose the wrong path.

277
00:20:25,360 --> 00:20:27,480
Just like how you never chose me.

278
00:20:29,120 --> 00:20:32,640
Right now, you don't stand a chance
against Phoenix.

279
00:20:33,640 --> 00:20:36,760
Stop fighting and run.

280
00:20:38,200 --> 00:20:40,320
Run while I can still repay you.

281
00:20:46,560 --> 00:20:47,840
I didn't choose the wrong path.

282
00:20:49,560 --> 00:20:50,960
I knew.

283
00:20:51,040 --> 00:20:53,120
I knew you were ambitious.

284
00:20:54,280 --> 00:20:56,280
But if you want to be better,

285
00:20:56,360 --> 00:20:59,560
choose a better path,
not the one that hurts others.

286
00:21:00,160 --> 00:21:01,160
Sarge.

287
00:21:02,400 --> 00:21:03,960
Consider this a warning.

288
00:21:05,520 --> 00:21:06,880
If you don't listen,

289
00:21:07,800 --> 00:21:09,400
I'll hand you over to Phoenix.

290
00:21:13,680 --> 00:21:15,200
Then do what you must.

291
00:21:19,920 --> 00:21:23,960
Stop working for Phoenix.
I don't want you as my enemy.

292
00:21:26,040 --> 00:21:29,400
If you didn't want my life,
why did you stop me that day?

293
00:21:31,840 --> 00:21:33,240
If you don't believe me,

294
00:21:34,160 --> 00:21:36,200
let's say I don't owe you anything.

295
00:21:37,320 --> 00:21:39,080
Why is Praew here?

296
00:21:39,760 --> 00:21:41,040
Who's in there with her?

297
00:21:48,760 --> 00:21:53,480
If you really want to repay me,
decide which side you're on.

298
00:21:54,760 --> 00:21:55,680
Sarge!

299
00:22:07,960 --> 00:22:09,520
Everything's destroyed.

300
00:22:10,040 --> 00:22:12,320
Burned. Blown apart.

301
00:22:12,400 --> 00:22:16,120
All gambling sites have been hacked
beyond recovery.

302
00:22:16,960 --> 00:22:20,280
Money in the system
was auto-refunded to victims.

303
00:22:21,560 --> 00:22:22,520
What?

304
00:22:23,040 --> 00:22:26,560
They didn't just hit us where it hurts.

305
00:22:28,000 --> 00:22:30,080
They tried to play superhero.

306
00:22:30,160 --> 00:22:32,040
I asked the ones we captured.

307
00:22:32,800 --> 00:22:36,000
They call themselves "The Seven Legends."

308
00:22:37,520 --> 00:22:38,840
The Seven Legends?

309
00:22:39,560 --> 00:22:41,640
In real life, no one wants to be a hero.

310
00:22:41,720 --> 00:22:43,760
They're definitely government-backed.

311
00:23:16,840 --> 00:23:17,880
What are you doing, Beauty?

312
00:23:20,360 --> 00:23:21,320
Praew.

313
00:23:22,360 --> 00:23:23,200
What are you looking for?

314
00:23:25,080 --> 00:23:29,040
I followed you myself.
Arab's suspicious of you,

315
00:23:29,120 --> 00:23:31,000
but he couldn't touch you.

316
00:23:31,080 --> 00:23:33,680
So he ordered me to tail you.

317
00:23:33,760 --> 00:23:35,000
And it's just like he thought.

318
00:23:35,080 --> 00:23:37,680
You're a mole, working with Natee.

319
00:23:39,560 --> 00:23:40,960
I'm not a mole.

320
00:23:41,920 --> 00:23:44,320
And that guy you met,
the one you called "Sarge,"

321
00:23:44,840 --> 00:23:46,080
who is he?

322
00:23:55,480 --> 00:23:57,280
- Give it to me, Beauty.
- No!

323
00:24:07,960 --> 00:24:08,920
What is this?

324
00:24:09,440 --> 00:24:12,320
You said you weren't a mole.
Then what's this?

325
00:24:13,480 --> 00:24:14,880
- Beauty, stay out of it.
- Stop.

326
00:24:15,680 --> 00:24:17,320
Natee's Death File.

327
00:24:17,400 --> 00:24:20,920
You kept this and let Arab torture me?

328
00:24:22,840 --> 00:24:23,680
Give it to me.

329
00:24:24,280 --> 00:24:26,600
- Stop. Let go.
- Beauty, let go.

330
00:24:37,680 --> 00:24:39,400
Ms. Duangnet's been detained, Sarge?

331
00:24:41,080 --> 00:24:43,040
Where, Sarge? We'll go help.

332
00:24:45,800 --> 00:24:46,640
I don't know.

333
00:24:46,720 --> 00:24:48,600
- Oh?
- Oh, Sarge?

334
00:24:48,680 --> 00:24:50,200
Then where've you been?

335
00:24:51,680 --> 00:24:52,520
Yeah.

336
00:24:53,040 --> 00:24:54,600
- Akki.
- Hm?

337
00:24:54,680 --> 00:24:58,840
Are you sure
this intel leads us to Phoenix?

338
00:24:59,720 --> 00:25:00,720
Absolutely, Sarge.

339
00:25:00,800 --> 00:25:02,800
It's layered deep,

340
00:25:02,880 --> 00:25:05,400
but it confirms Phoenix is coming here.

341
00:25:05,480 --> 00:25:06,640
Good.

342
00:25:08,040 --> 00:25:10,360
Then I'm opening a manhunt on Phoenix

343
00:25:11,120 --> 00:25:13,480
to bring Ms. Duangnet back.

344
00:26:31,560 --> 00:26:33,200
Hey, Akki.

345
00:26:33,280 --> 00:26:37,360
What kind of binoculars are these?
It's pitch-black. I can't see anything.

346
00:26:37,960 --> 00:26:39,200
Can't see at all.

347
00:26:39,720 --> 00:26:41,760
Hey, Sarge. Remove the lens caps.

348
00:26:43,200 --> 00:26:44,320
Why didn't you take them off for me?

349
00:26:45,920 --> 00:26:47,600
That's my team leader.

350
00:26:48,640 --> 00:26:50,240
I don't see a damn thing.

351
00:26:50,960 --> 00:26:52,560
Your intel is legit or what?

352
00:26:52,640 --> 00:26:54,240
Sarge.

353
00:26:54,320 --> 00:26:57,280
Spoofing GPS into a trap isn't easy.

354
00:26:57,360 --> 00:26:58,880
You've gotta allow for system error.

355
00:27:00,200 --> 00:27:03,320
And our lives are riding
on your system error?

356
00:27:03,400 --> 00:27:06,360
I didn't say it would have an error.

357
00:27:06,440 --> 00:27:07,720
It's just in case.

358
00:27:08,440 --> 00:27:11,080
But this isn't a game. We can't restart.

359
00:27:11,160 --> 00:27:13,360
Then don't die stupidly.

360
00:27:13,440 --> 00:27:14,560
Oh, my friend.

361
00:27:14,640 --> 00:27:16,640
That mouth's asking for a hit.

362
00:27:16,720 --> 00:27:18,320
So what? Bring it. Anytime.

363
00:27:18,400 --> 00:27:20,200
- Bring it.
- Come on.

364
00:27:20,280 --> 00:27:21,440
- You won't stop?
- Come on.

365
00:27:21,520 --> 00:27:22,680
Hey, enough! Stop.

366
00:27:23,920 --> 00:27:25,240
If you wanna fight, punch me.

367
00:27:25,320 --> 00:27:26,160
- Sure, Sarge.
- Yeah.

368
00:27:26,680 --> 00:27:27,520
No!

369
00:27:28,200 --> 00:27:29,400
Be serious.

370
00:27:32,720 --> 00:27:33,640
Where's Juk?

371
00:27:33,720 --> 00:27:34,840
Here, Sarge.

372
00:27:35,520 --> 00:27:36,760
- Hey.
- Hey.

373
00:27:39,120 --> 00:27:41,880
The bomb of faith is ready, Sarge.

374
00:27:42,840 --> 00:27:43,920
This kid's got guts.

375
00:27:48,800 --> 00:27:49,760
Juk.

376
00:27:50,480 --> 00:27:51,600
They're coming.

377
00:27:54,280 --> 00:27:55,920
<i>Kla, how's it over there?</i>

378
00:27:59,520 --> 00:28:00,880
Oh, Sarge.

379
00:28:00,960 --> 00:28:03,520
This is easy. No worries.

380
00:28:04,560 --> 00:28:06,360
<i>Moh, Dan, how's it there?</i>

381
00:28:07,640 --> 00:28:11,200
What's up, Sarge?
I've been waiting so long I need to poop.

382
00:28:13,680 --> 00:28:14,760
Moh.

383
00:28:15,760 --> 00:28:16,960
What the hell are you doing?

384
00:28:17,040 --> 00:28:19,400
- Camouflage.
- All right. Give me one.

385
00:28:19,480 --> 00:28:21,720
Yeah. Camouflage. They'll never see us.

386
00:28:21,800 --> 00:28:23,000
Are you insane?

387
00:28:24,320 --> 00:28:25,440
Be serious.

388
00:28:25,520 --> 00:28:28,920
Enough screwing around!
They're here. Get ready.

389
00:28:39,520 --> 00:28:42,080
<i>All units, get ready.</i>
<i>Target's approaching.</i>

390
00:28:47,720 --> 00:28:48,840
Juk.

391
00:28:49,480 --> 00:28:50,880
On three, then detonate.

392
00:28:52,600 --> 00:28:53,560
One.

393
00:28:55,200 --> 00:28:56,160
Three!

394
00:29:03,720 --> 00:29:05,240
Where the hell did two go, Sarge?

395
00:29:21,000 --> 00:29:21,840
See?

396
00:29:21,920 --> 00:29:24,560
Easy peasy, lemon squeezy.

397
00:29:50,680 --> 00:29:51,520
Hey, how is it?

398
00:29:51,600 --> 00:29:52,520
Nothing.

399
00:29:57,120 --> 00:29:58,280
- Hey!
- Hey!

400
00:30:07,640 --> 00:30:09,440
I'm here to help!

401
00:30:09,520 --> 00:30:10,800
- Hey.
- Whoa.

402
00:30:18,440 --> 00:30:20,120
- Tired?
- Why're you riding his back?

403
00:30:21,120 --> 00:30:22,680
Walking's not cool enough.

404
00:30:23,680 --> 00:30:24,520
Found this in the van.

405
00:30:24,600 --> 00:30:25,520
- All right.
- Nice.

406
00:30:25,600 --> 00:30:26,920
- Good.
- Dump the old one.

407
00:30:27,000 --> 00:30:28,000
- Big one.
- Yeah.

408
00:30:28,080 --> 00:30:30,360
Hey, all of you, die now!

409
00:30:30,440 --> 00:30:31,680
- Shit!
- Hey!

410
00:30:35,680 --> 00:30:36,800
- Whoa.
- Sarge.

411
00:30:36,880 --> 00:30:37,720
Huh?

412
00:30:38,480 --> 00:30:40,000
- Let's go.
- We survived.

413
00:30:40,080 --> 00:30:41,480
- This is how it should be.
- Yeah.

414
00:30:41,560 --> 00:30:42,440
You guys okay?

415
00:30:42,520 --> 00:30:43,680
- We're okay.
- We're okay.

416
00:30:43,760 --> 00:30:45,040
- Good.
- Yeah.

417
00:30:45,120 --> 00:30:46,160
But I'm not okay.

418
00:30:46,920 --> 00:30:48,280
Why?

419
00:30:56,320 --> 00:30:58,000
Your dad's here. I'm out.

420
00:30:59,440 --> 00:31:00,280
- Hey!
- Huh?

421
00:31:00,360 --> 00:31:01,080
- Sarge!
- Sarge!

422
00:31:01,160 --> 00:31:02,080
Hey, Sarge!

423
00:31:02,160 --> 00:31:03,280
- Hurry up.
- Hurry up.

424
00:31:03,360 --> 00:31:04,240
Come on.

425
00:31:06,480 --> 00:31:08,760
There are only three cars.
Why are there a lot of them?

426
00:31:08,840 --> 00:31:09,960
And where's Phoenix?

427
00:31:10,040 --> 00:31:13,280
Akki, did they find out
we hacked the system?

428
00:31:13,360 --> 00:31:14,560
It's fine.

429
00:31:14,640 --> 00:31:17,000
We're this far, no turning back.

430
00:31:17,520 --> 00:31:19,280
Seven Legends, go!

431
00:31:23,080 --> 00:31:24,720
This way, you idiots!

432
00:31:26,640 --> 00:31:27,600
Cowards.

433
00:31:28,400 --> 00:31:29,240
Fine.

434
00:31:29,880 --> 00:31:31,240
I'll show you my trick shot.

435
00:31:56,960 --> 00:31:58,280
How's that, huh?

436
00:32:02,480 --> 00:32:04,480
I never should've taken this job.

437
00:32:09,360 --> 00:32:10,920
- Whoa.
- Hey.

438
00:32:14,200 --> 00:32:14,840
- Hey.
- Hey.

439
00:32:14,920 --> 00:32:16,520
- Hey.
- Sarge.

440
00:32:16,600 --> 00:32:17,320
- Sarge.
- Sarge.

441
00:32:17,400 --> 00:32:18,240
- Sarge.
- Let's check on him.

442
00:32:18,320 --> 00:32:19,320
- Sarge.
- Let's go help him.

443
00:32:22,160 --> 00:32:23,000
- Sarge!
- Sarge.

444
00:32:23,080 --> 00:32:24,040
- Sarge.
- Sarge.

445
00:32:24,120 --> 00:32:25,640
- Hey.
- Where'd Sarge go?

446
00:32:38,640 --> 00:32:40,400
Arab must get this intel.

447
00:32:43,280 --> 00:32:44,240
Hey.

448
00:32:48,920 --> 00:32:50,760
You're just a mole.

449
00:32:51,360 --> 00:32:54,800
If Boss finds out,
I'll be his woman for sure.

450
00:32:55,400 --> 00:32:56,560
Where are you going?

451
00:33:01,240 --> 00:33:03,240
You… You betrayed Boss.

452
00:33:04,000 --> 00:33:05,800
I didn't betray him.

453
00:33:05,880 --> 00:33:07,440
I just wanted to fix things

454
00:33:07,520 --> 00:33:09,600
and protect the man who saved my life.

455
00:33:10,600 --> 00:33:13,120
But you wanted the spotlight for yourself.

456
00:33:13,200 --> 00:33:14,800
So I had to protect myself.

457
00:33:16,040 --> 00:33:17,800
Boss isn't stupid.

458
00:33:17,880 --> 00:33:20,200
He'll never believe someone like you.

459
00:33:23,280 --> 00:33:24,280
Oh yeah?

460
00:33:24,800 --> 00:33:26,480
- Don't.
- Let go.

461
00:33:26,560 --> 00:33:27,920
- No.
- Let go.

462
00:33:34,760 --> 00:33:36,000
I didn't lie to Boss.

463
00:33:36,520 --> 00:33:39,600
I just wanted to return the Death File.

464
00:33:40,120 --> 00:33:42,640
Then I'd be the loyal one.

465
00:33:42,720 --> 00:33:44,040
And you

466
00:33:44,560 --> 00:33:46,640
would be the traitor.

467
00:33:46,720 --> 00:33:47,800
That's it.

468
00:34:11,560 --> 00:34:12,480
Let go of me.

469
00:34:16,280 --> 00:34:18,960
Stop making things harder for yourself.

470
00:34:20,600 --> 00:34:21,960
I'm sorry, Boss.

471
00:34:25,159 --> 00:34:28,880
Is an apology really enough?

472
00:34:29,920 --> 00:34:34,120
You know my biggest money-maker

473
00:34:34,639 --> 00:34:37,920
are online networks and call center scams.

474
00:34:39,520 --> 00:34:42,600
That's why I picked
the person I trusted most to run them.

475
00:34:43,800 --> 00:34:46,760
Looks like I was wrong.

476
00:34:47,280 --> 00:34:50,320
Boss, they're rookie agents.

477
00:34:50,400 --> 00:34:52,199
No records in the system.

478
00:34:53,040 --> 00:34:55,360
Oh? Really?

479
00:34:56,120 --> 00:34:59,360
So you got careless.
Is that what you're saying?

480
00:34:59,440 --> 00:35:01,400
No, Boss.

481
00:35:01,480 --> 00:35:03,560
They fell into my trap.

482
00:35:03,640 --> 00:35:06,600
Their leader, Sergeant Dab Jampoh,

483
00:35:06,680 --> 00:35:08,680
was blown to pieces.

484
00:35:08,760 --> 00:35:10,560
And the Seven Legends team

485
00:35:10,640 --> 00:35:13,720
is being hunted
in every corner of Pha Mok.

486
00:35:13,800 --> 00:35:16,200
They'll never regroup again.

487
00:35:16,280 --> 00:35:19,560
That's your problem
to deal with from the start, isn't it?

488
00:35:24,120 --> 00:35:25,200
You know

489
00:35:25,720 --> 00:35:27,640
what was destroyed

490
00:35:27,720 --> 00:35:29,720
wasn't just my money.

491
00:35:30,240 --> 00:35:33,480
It's affecting
the most important deal of my life,

492
00:35:33,560 --> 00:35:35,920
the one that's about to happen.

493
00:35:36,000 --> 00:35:37,040
Boss.

494
00:35:37,120 --> 00:35:39,800
I know this matters to you.

495
00:35:40,640 --> 00:35:41,840
You value trust.

496
00:35:41,920 --> 00:35:45,400
Boss, I promise, the Seven Legends

497
00:35:45,480 --> 00:35:47,800
will never bother you again!

498
00:35:47,880 --> 00:35:49,440
Boss. Boss.

499
00:35:50,120 --> 00:35:54,000
Good. You admitted your mistake.

500
00:35:56,000 --> 00:35:56,960
But

501
00:35:57,840 --> 00:35:59,560
your words alone

502
00:36:00,400 --> 00:36:02,400
aren't enough to guarantee anything.

503
00:36:15,160 --> 00:36:18,120
Fortunately,
you've worked for me a long time.

504
00:36:18,640 --> 00:36:20,840
So this is the price you have to pay.

505
00:36:34,640 --> 00:36:36,400
I forgive you.

506
00:36:37,200 --> 00:36:41,240
But you have to eliminate
the Seven Legends.

507
00:36:41,880 --> 00:36:43,360
Kill them all

508
00:36:44,440 --> 00:36:48,680
before the big launch
of the Pha Mok City Project.

509
00:36:54,160 --> 00:36:57,320
Yes, Boss. I promise.
I know what to do now.

510
00:36:57,840 --> 00:36:59,080
Good.

511
00:36:59,720 --> 00:37:03,760
You get to continue with the deal
that will reshape my business.

512
00:37:04,760 --> 00:37:06,760
As for the others…

513
00:37:06,840 --> 00:37:09,280
What about Praewpan and Beauty?

514
00:37:14,040 --> 00:37:15,480
Those two

515
00:37:16,080 --> 00:37:17,680
are useless to me now.

516
00:37:49,320 --> 00:37:50,400
Boss,

517
00:37:51,200 --> 00:37:52,880
I would never betray you.

518
00:37:52,960 --> 00:37:53,960
Please let me go.

519
00:37:57,360 --> 00:37:58,840
I had to go through this.

520
00:37:59,360 --> 00:38:03,160
Only words aren't enough anymore.

521
00:38:07,280 --> 00:38:09,760
If you have proof I'm a spy,

522
00:38:09,840 --> 00:38:11,000
then show me.

523
00:38:12,120 --> 00:38:13,800
I can't escape anyway.

524
00:38:19,720 --> 00:38:23,080
But if you're looking for a scapegoat,
don't choose me.

525
00:38:24,600 --> 00:38:26,600
I've been loyal to you all along.

526
00:38:27,520 --> 00:38:28,800
Shut up.

527
00:38:29,640 --> 00:38:31,880
Boss is running out of patience.

528
00:38:32,560 --> 00:38:36,360
I must prove whether you're really a spy.

529
00:39:00,840 --> 00:39:03,120
<i>The Seven Legends fell into my trap.</i>

530
00:39:06,400 --> 00:39:08,800
Sergeant Dab was blown to pieces.

531
00:39:09,760 --> 00:39:12,000
The rest are being hunted.

532
00:39:18,880 --> 00:39:20,760
- Hey!
- Mr. Dan.

533
00:39:43,080 --> 00:39:44,400
We're here.

534
00:39:44,920 --> 00:39:46,240
Let's take every last one.

535
00:40:02,040 --> 00:40:03,640
Cut. Okay.

536
00:40:10,640 --> 00:40:11,680
Hey!

537
00:40:12,200 --> 00:40:13,280
Why are you yelling?

538
00:40:13,360 --> 00:40:14,680
Hey, run!

539
00:40:14,760 --> 00:40:16,400
- Let's go!
- Hurry!

540
00:40:24,000 --> 00:40:25,040
Cut.

541
00:40:31,920 --> 00:40:33,520
Yeah.

542
00:40:35,400 --> 00:40:36,720
Run!

543
00:40:36,800 --> 00:40:38,600
Hey!

544
00:40:38,680 --> 00:40:40,120
Run! Go!

545
00:40:40,200 --> 00:40:41,280
Hey!

546
00:40:41,360 --> 00:40:42,400
Here.

547
00:40:42,480 --> 00:40:44,360
Stop right here. If I do this,

548
00:40:44,440 --> 00:40:46,400
it will hit. See?

549
00:40:46,480 --> 00:40:48,360
- See?
- Yes.

550
00:40:48,440 --> 00:40:50,120
- Go ahead.
- Okay.

551
00:40:50,200 --> 00:40:52,200
- Hurry.
- Okay.

552
00:40:52,280 --> 00:40:53,880
Yeah.

553
00:40:53,960 --> 00:40:56,640
Look at the camera. Good.

554
00:40:56,720 --> 00:40:59,600
Come this way. Like that!

555
00:41:00,120 --> 00:41:01,280
- Give it to me.
- You guys okay?

556
00:41:01,360 --> 00:41:02,800
- We're okay, Sarge.
- Good.

557
00:41:02,880 --> 00:41:04,280
- Good.
- But I'm not okay.

558
00:41:04,360 --> 00:41:05,360
- Oh.
- Oh, why, Sarge?

559
00:41:06,080 --> 00:41:07,200
Next, enemy incoming.

560
00:41:07,280 --> 00:41:08,640
- Huh?
- I'm out.

561
00:41:08,720 --> 00:41:09,760
- Sarge?
- Sarge?

562
00:41:18,320 --> 00:41:23,120
